---
title: Rustic Bison and Mushroom Cottage Pie with Fresh Salad
description: Few dishes exemplify comfort food quite like a cottage pie! This version is filled with super-flavourful ingredients like bison and mixed mushrooms, then topped with aged cheddar. A simple fresh salad on the side completes this cozy dinner at home!

